name.ja: オオヤツ・ツマムヒメ

text.en: Once per turn, when a card or effect is activated that targets this card, or when this card is targeted for an attack (Quick Effect): You can Special Summon 1 "Oyatsu Token" (Plant/LIGHT/Level 1/ATK 800/DEF 800). Once per turn, when your opponent would Special Summon a monster(s) (Quick Effect): You can Tribute 1 Normal Monster; negate the Summon, and if you do, destroy that monster(s).
